Use the standard library
This is how to max_fill of grid and capacity:
   Remember that total is 0
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this grid's length times:
      Remember that row is item i in grid
      Remember that j is 0
      Remember that filled is 0
      Do this row's length times:
         When item j in row is 1, then:
            Increase filled
         End when
         Increase j
      End do
      Remember that buckets is quotient of filled and capacity
      When remainder of filled and capacity is more than 0, then:
         Increase buckets
      End when
      Remember that total is sum of total and buckets
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is total
Now you know